# Privacy Policy

**Arivu Kids Quiz**

Effective Date: 2026

Arivu Kids Quiz (“we”, “our”, or “us”) is designed to provide a safe and fun learning experience for children. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle user information.

## 1. Information We Collect

We do **not collect, store, or share any personal information** from users.

The app works completely offline and does not require users to sign in or provide any personal data.

