Our app is specifically designed for children under the age of 13. We strictly comply with child safety guidelines and do not collect any personal information from children.

## 3. Internet Usage

Arivu Kids Quiz works fully offline. The app does not require an internet connection to function and does not transmit any data externally.

## 4. Third-Party Services

This app does not use any third-party services, analytics tools, or advertising networks.

## 5. Data Security

Since we do not collect any user data, there is no risk of data misuse or unauthorized access.

